gobuster (Directory/File, DNS and VHost busting tool written in Go)

Gobuster is a high-performance directory/file, DNS and virtual host
brute-forcing tool written in Go. It's designed to be fast, reliable,
and easy to use for security professionals and penetration testers.

HOME: https://github.com/OJ/gobuster

